---
// Services Component
---

<section id="services" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[#464237] rough-texture">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <!-- Section Title -->
    <div class="text-center mb-20 fade-up">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
        NOUVATIONが提供する<br class="md:hidden" />4つのサービス
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-[#d5db00] mx-auto mt-6"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-24">
      <!-- Service 01: Market Graph -->
      <article class="bg-[#464237]/80 border border-[#d5db00]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 fade-up hover:border-[#d5db00]/40 transition-all">
        <span class="font-display text-6xl font-bold text-[#d5db00]/20 block mb-6">01</span>
        
        <div class="mb-10 max-w-3xl">
          <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
            「生きた数字」が見える。<br />迷いが消える。
          </h3>
          
          <p class="text-[#d5db00] font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center">
            <svg class="mr-2" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            市場価格推移グラフ
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-white leading-loose">
            全国7市場・14品目の価格情報を一元化。<br />
            過去データと比較することで、意思決定（出荷タイミング）の自信に繋がります。
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="border border-[#d5db00]/30 rounded-2xl p-8 bg-[#464237] h-80 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-center">
            <svg class="mx-auto mb-4 text-[#d5db00]" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-white/60">Interactive Graph UI</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 02: Instagram -->
      <article class="bg-[#464237]/80 border border-[#d5db00]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 fade-up hover:border-[#d5db00]/40 transition-all">
        <span class="font-display text-6xl font-bold text-[#d5db00]/20 block mb-6">02</span>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
              選ばれている理由は<br />その「質」
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-[#d5db00] font-bold text-lg mb-6 flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-2" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></rect>
                <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
                <line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></line>
              </svg>
              Instagramメディア
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 text-white leading-loose">
              <p>
                農家・農業関係者の年齢層が16~64歳で96%を占めており、次世代を担う若手・現役プレイヤーにリーチできます。
              </p>
              <p>
                また、農家・農業関係者比率が約8割。<br />
                農業界でも数少ない"実働世代向け"メディアとして、高い行動率（エンゲージメント）を誇ります。
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-8 p-6 bg-[#464237] border border-[#d5db00]/30 rounded-2xl inline-block">
              <div class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-[#d5db00]">
                17,500<span class="text-2xl">+</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-normal text-white/60 ml-2">Followers</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-[#464237] aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl border border-[#d5db00]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="text-[#d5db00]/50" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></rect>
                <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#464237] aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl border border-[#d5db00]/20 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="text-[#d5db00]/50" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></rect>
                <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 03: AI Support -->
      <article class="bg-[#464237]/80 border border-[#d5db00]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden fade-up hover:border-[#d5db00]/40 transition-all">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-[#d5db00] text-[#352421] text-xs font-bold px-6 py-2 rounded-bl-2xl">
          COMING SOON
        </div>
        
        <span class="font-display text-6xl font-bold text-[#d5db00]/20 block mb-6">03</span>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
              栽培の悩みも、<br />補助金のことも。<br />
              「誰に聞けばいいか<br class="hidden md:block" />分からない」を無くします。
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-[#d5db00] font-bold text-lg mb-6 flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-2" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
              </svg>
              農業AI専用サポート
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-white leading-loose mb-4">
              栽培技術から補助金申請まで。24時間365日、あなたの疑問に即座に応えるパートナーAI。
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-sm text-white/60">※現在サービス構築中です</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-[#464237] rounded-2xl border border-[#d5db00]/30 p-8 h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg class="mx-auto mb-4 text-[#d5db00]" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></rect>
                <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-white/60">AI Chat Interface</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Service 04: Web Production -->
      <article class="bg-[#464237]/80 border border-[#d5db00]/20 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 fade-up hover:border-[#d5db00]/40 transition-all">
        <span class="font-display text-6xl font-bold text-[#d5db00]/20 block mb-6">04</span>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1 bg-[#464237] rounded-2xl border border-[#d5db00]/30 p-8 h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <svg class="mx-auto mb-4 text-[#d5db00]" width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
                <path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
                <path d="M2 2l7.586 7.586" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
                <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></circle>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-white/60">Web Design Mockup</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-relaxed text-white">
              農業の現場を知る<br />私たちだから、<br />
              想いが伝わるHPが<br class="hidden md:block" />作れる。
            </h3>
            
            <p class="text-[#d5db00] font-bold text-lg mb-6 flex items-center">
              <svg class="mr-2" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <path d="M12 19l7-7 3 3-7 7-3-3z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
                <path d="M18 13l-1.5-7.5L2 2l3.5 14.5L13 18l5-5z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"></path>
              </svg>
              農業特化型Web制作
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4 text-white leading-loose">
              <p>
                「ITはよく分からない」という方でもご安心ください。農業界の知見とWebの技術を持つ私たちが、ヒアリングから公開まで丸ごとサポートします。
              </p>
              <p>
                採用強化や販路拡大に必要な機能を絞り込み、高品質かつリーズナブルな価格で提供します。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>